Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:05.46,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.5}行ってみよ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.46,0:03:06.29,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:06.29,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.5}うん
Dialogue: 1,0:03:07.50,0:03:12.17,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}脚畔芝樱盛开 远处武甲山耸立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:12.17,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}足元に芝桜　向こうには武甲山
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.76,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}但我既不拍花 也不拍山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.76,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}なのに山でも花でもなく
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.76,0:03:18.26,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}却在这拍露天小摊 是否有点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:18.26,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}出店撮ってる私って一体
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.14,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}管它的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.14,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}ま　いっか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.23,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.15,0:03:30.23,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}いた
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.54,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}这么好喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.54,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}おいしそ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.73,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord3}为啥说「让她去真的好吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.73,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord3}「行かせてよかったの」って何
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.77,0:05:38.53,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord3}伊吹她啊 很大「可能」就是喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:38.53,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord3}だっていぶき　多分「アレ」　お酒飲んでるでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.53,0:05:42.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord3}但她可不乐意喝酒的时候给人瞧见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:42.74,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord3}彼女　お酒飲んでるところ　人に見られるの嫌いじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.5}至于为什么 就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.07,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.5}なんでか知らないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.37,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E}{\blur0.7\bord2}协管 你打嗝可真响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:52.37,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E}{\blur0.7\bord2}あの　寮長さん　立派なしゃっくりですね
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&37375547476E\blur0.7\bord2.3}协管 你打嗝可真响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:54.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&37375547476E\blur0.7\bord2.3}あの　寮長さん　立派なしゃっくりですね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.88,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E}{\blur0.7\bord2}在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.88,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E}{\blur0.7\bord2}寮長さん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.60,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}你是大一那个 上伊那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.60,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}ちょっ…ひっく　1年の　上伊那さん
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.81,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}等会 抱歉 我刚喝了酒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:12.81,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}待　ごめ　飲んだから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.90,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E}{\blur0.7\bord2}懂了 这是喝酒喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.90,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E}{\blur0.7\bord2}お酒飲むとしゃっくり出ちゃうんですね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.44,0:06:23.07,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2.25}被人看见丢死人了 所以我才老是一个人喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:23.07,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2.25}失礼だし　恥ずかしいから人前で飲めないの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.91,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2.25}说来自己酒瘾倒也大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.91,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2.25}お酒は好きなんだけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.16,0:06:30.83,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&585887\4c&585887}{\blur0.7\bord2}我也挺想试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:30.83,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&585887\4c&585887}{\blur0.7\bord2}私もそれ　飲んでみたいな
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.58,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.58,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}ダメですか
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.67,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}我看你吨吨吨很爽的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.67,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}寮長さんがあんまりおいしそうに飲むから
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}也就觉得「蛮有意思」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.67,0:06:38.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}「いいな」って思って
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.55,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}你能喝酒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.55,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}上伊那さん　お酒飲めるの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.18,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&26263B\4c&26263B\blur0.7\bord2}法定年龄倒是过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:45.18,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&26263B\4c&26263B\blur0.7\bord2}法律的には　飲めます
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&26263B\4c&26263B\blur0.7\bord2}我复读了一年嘛 现在满二十了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.43,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&26263B\4c&26263B\blur0.7\bord2}私　浪人してて　今20歳なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.43,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.2}酒力好不好就不一定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.43,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.2}体質的には　わかんないです
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.43,0:06:55.94,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}毕竟我一次都没喝过呢 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:55.94,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}なにせ　一度も飲んだことないので
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.99,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}在你眼里 我喝酒的样子很享受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.99,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2.2}…私　そんなに美味しそうに飲んでた
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.95,0:07:10.45,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord3}你不介意的话 我这杯嗨棒剩点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:10.45,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord3}いいよ　飲みさしのハイボールでよければ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.08,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.08,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.80,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.8}这是间接接吻了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.80,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.8}間接キスだね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.51,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.8}你这话说的 上头了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.51,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.8}酔ってます
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.52,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&26263B\4c&26263B\blur0.7\bord2.5}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.52,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&26263B\4c&26263B\blur0.7\bord2.5}ど…　どう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2}好多气泡 其他的味道就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.48,0:07:38.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2}しゅわしゅわしてよくわから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.02,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2}好多气泡 其他的味道就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:39.02,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2}しゅわしゅわしてよくわから
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.86,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2}我不大能接受碳酸饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:47.86,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2}炭酸　苦手なんです
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.74,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}我们似乎没差诶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:52.74,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}私たち　おそろいですねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.41,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.41,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}うん
Dialogue: 1,0:07:56.33,0:07:58.96,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}你不用这么担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:58.96,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}あんまり気にしない方がいいですよ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.84,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}任谁都会打嗝的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.96,0:08:01.84,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}しゃっくりもげっぷも誰だってしますし
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.92,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}这学妹可真是个小棉袄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.92,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}気の使える良い後輩が入ってきたな
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}嗯 你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:08.97,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}うん　そうだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.97,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.97,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}ねっ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.98,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}不过你也挺小气的 吃独食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.98,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2.5}それにしても寮長はズルいですねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.48,0:08:22.69,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}喝这么好喝的 都不带她们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:22.69,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755\blur0.7\bord2}こんなおいしいの　ひとりで飲んでたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E}{\blur0.7\bord2}你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E}{\blur0.7\bord2}寮長って
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.70,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}人还怪可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.70,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}寮長ってかわいいですね
Dialogue: 1,0:08:38.91,0:08:43.13,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2}我刚刚说「蛮有意思」 是说你 不是说喝酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:43.13,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&373755\4c&373755}{\blur0.7\bord2}さっきの「いいな」は　寮長が「いいな」ってイミですよ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.42,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}你这是在逗我玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.42,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}何よ　それ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.30,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}醉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.30,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}酔ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.63,Dial-CHI,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}人家不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.30,0:08:47.63,Dial-JPN,,0,0,0,,{\c&ffffff\3c&47476E\4c&47476E\blur0.7\bord2}知りませんよぉ
